[79.885202, "o", "\r\n  nono v0.20.0\r\n  Capabilities:\r\n  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n       + 45 system/group paths (-v to show)\r\n   net  outbound allowed\r\n  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n   kernel  Landlock V4 (File rename across directories (Refer), File truncation (Truncate), TCP network filtering)\r\n          degraded: IoctlDev, Scoping (upgrade kernel for full support)\r\n  Applying sandbox... active\r\n\r\n============================================\r\n Mode: SANDBOX (runtimeClassName: nono-sandbox)\r\n Profile: default — Landlock filesystem isolation\r\n============================================\r\n\r\n--- attack surface (expected: BLOCKED by Landlock) ---\r\n  write /etc/hosts (host poisoning)                 BLOCKED\r\n  write /usr/local/bin/exploit (backdoor)           BLOCKED\r\n  read /etc/shadow (credential theft)               BLOCKED\r\n  read /etc/passwd (user enumeration)               BLOCKED\r\n  write site-packages/evil.py (pkg inject)          BLOCKED\r\n\r\n--- python-dev runtime (expected: ALLOWED) ---\r\n  python3 --version                                 ALLOWED\r\n  python3 -c print                                  ALLOWED\r\n  write /tmp/workfile                               ALLOWED\r\n\r\nDone.\r\n"]
